description:
THERE IS A LOT going on in the Housewives cinematic universe this week. First, Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills finale, which featured a Dorit party and a Denise/Rinna sitdown for the ages. On Real Housewives of New York, the women celebrate Leah's fashions and Dorinda's last birthday as a Housewife. :( Plus, Garcelle joins The Real and Maloof returns!
